From the IDEAS-3 project:

Prior to flight
 - open chat room (with logging)
 - get surface and upper air charts

During flight
 - get surface charts every half hour

one hour after flight
 - get satellite loops (vis and IR) to encompass entire flight time
 unpack loops (goes.proc script) to prepare for web display

after data available
 - archive raw ads, 2d, CPI and MCR
 - update tapes.ppp
 - post netCDF, 2d (and other requested) files to FTP site (gzipped)
 - update "data_access.html" file
 - update "flights.html" file
 - create whole-flight plots using ncplot
 - update FltMatrix.html
 - edit (if necessary) and post xchat log
